"{\"uid\": \"nzherald.co.nz-nz-olympic-rider-john-cottle-and-former-client-in-dispute-over-unpaid-bill-for-arena-construction-RSYNYVASZNB5LDABVOAGN2H4CE\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"A top Olympic equestrian and the woman who commissioned him to work on a horse training arena are at loggerheads over an almost $14,000 debt she refuses to pay, despite a court order.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A top Olympic equestrian\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 24}, {\"ngram\": \"the woman\", \"from\": 29, \"to\": 38}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse training arena\", \"from\": 71, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"loggerheads\", \"from\": 101, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"an almost $14,000 debt\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 140}, {\"ngram\": \"a court order\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 1984 and 1988 Olympian, John Cottle, who is among the country's most highly regarded ridersand trainers, says he has all but written off the money owed by former client Raine Selles, who complained about problems with a training arena he resurfaced.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 205, \"end\": 213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999848896551, \"rank\": 1.4337124405719285e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 5.248797782203521e-13, \"text\": \"Selles\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"John Cottle\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 226}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's most highly regarded ridersand trainers\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"a training arena\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cottle, whoquit his showjumping careerin 2006 and was inducted into the Equestrian Sports NZ Hall of Fame last year, says he's dismayed there are so few avenues for getting the money owed, other than further expensive legal action for enforcement.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"his showjumping careerin\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"the Equestrian Sports NZ Hall\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"Fame\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"so few avenues\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"further expensive legal action\", \"from\": 642, \"to\": 672}, {\"ngram\": \"enforcement\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles, who co-runs a business resolving disputes in the construction sector, was equally frustrated.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"a business resolving disputes\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction sector\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said she was familiar with construction and the law around it, and alleged there were \\\"many errors\\\" in how Cottle carried out the task.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"construction\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"the law\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"many errors\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"the task\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles confirmed to NZME that she would not be paying Cottle what was owed, despite an order from the district court.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"NZME\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 959}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 995}, {\"ngram\": \"an order\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the district court\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not paying him an absolute penny - or a dollar in this case, because as far as I am concerned, he owes me the losses,\\\" she claimed.\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an absolute penny\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"a dollar\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"the losses\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles, who now lives in Christchurch, commissioned Cottle in 2020 to source materials used to resurface the arena at the Auckland property she owned at the time.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"score\": 0.9999999050351153, \"rank\": 9.491612871623829e-08, \"text\": \"Auckland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"Christchurch\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1251}, {\"ngram\": \"materials\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement to NZME, she claims to have been forced to sell the property due to what happened.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Media_and_Entertainment\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NZME\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Media_and_Entertainment\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_Media_and_Entertainment\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"the property\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the legal decisions, the contract specified that the customer (Selles) was to prepare the laser-levelled compacted base, but when the contractor hired to do that then left, Selles asked Cottle to work on the base.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 5.248797782203521e-13, \"text\": \"Selles\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the legal decisions\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"the contract\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"the customer\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"the laser-levelled compacted base\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"the contractor\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1661}, {\"ngram\": \"the base\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cottle said that when Selles did not want to spend money on a full rebuild, which had been advised, he opted to carry out an agreed schedule of less intensive preparatory work, including the removal of surrounding lime rock, replace the membrane on drain lines with better-quality material, and work to enhance drainage.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 2004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 5.248797782203521e-13, \"text\": \"Selles\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"a full rebuild\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"an agreed schedule\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"less intensive preparatory work\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"the removal\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"lime rock\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"the membrane\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"drain lines\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"better-quality material\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1973}, {\"ngram\": \"drainage\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles later claimed Cottle performed works that levelled the base of the arena, but she produced no evidence to support that claim and neither did invoices provided by Cottle show any such work.\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"works\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"the base\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"no evidence\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"that claim\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2137}, {\"ngram\": \"neither\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"invoices\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2162}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"any such work\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When Selles refused to pay two invoices totalling $13,852, Cottle lodged a claim with the Disputes Tribunal.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"two invoices\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2242}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"a claim\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"the Disputes Tribunal\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles then lodged a counterclaim for $100,000 (plus GST).\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"a counterclaim\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"GST\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She alleged Cottle had made mistakes with the arena's design and asserted she was claiming her losses as a result of that.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"mistakes\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena's design\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"her losses\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles then reduced her counterclaim to $30,000 to bring it within the tribunal's monetary limit.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2501}, {\"ngram\": \"her counterclaim\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"the tribunal's monetary limit\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tribunal concluded that the work done by Cottle was carried out according to the contract.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tribunal\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"the contract\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It found that even if the arena was not ideal to be ridden on, that was not the fault of Cottle's company.\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"the fault\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle's company\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also said Selles' claim for money paid to others involved in the job, and the refund of the money already paid to Cottle, effectively amounted to \\\"double dipping\\\" - in other words, \\\"the work would have been done for nothing\\\".\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 3025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2810, \"end\": 2816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 5.248797782203521e-13, \"text\": \"Selles\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"the refund\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2884}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"double dipping\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"other words\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tribunal ordered Selles to pay Cottle the balance of two invoices for the supply of sand (for use in the arena surface mix) plus machinery hire and use.\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3048, \"end\": 3054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 5.248797782203521e-13, \"text\": \"Selles\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tribunal\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"two invoices\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"the supply\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3111}, {\"ngram\": \"sand\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena surface mix\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tribunal said that as a result, Selles' counterclaim failed.\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3221, \"end\": 3227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 5.248797782203521e-13, \"text\": \"Selles\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Selles-sur-Cher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tribunal\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3197}, {\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles appealed the decision to the Auckland District Court, on grounds that included the tribunal referee's \\\"lack of understanding and failure to grasp the issues\\\", and a breach of natural justice.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3287, \"end\": 3295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"score\": 0.9999999050351153, \"rank\": 9.491612871623829e-08, \"text\": \"Auckland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Auckland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"grounds\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3322}, {\"ngram\": \"the tribunal referee's \\\"lack\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3365}, {\"ngram\": \"understanding\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3382}, {\"ngram\": \"failure\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"the issues\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3414}, {\"ngram\": \"a breach\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3429}, {\"ngram\": \"natural justice\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles contended that the way the referee conducted the hearing was unfair and \\\"prejudicially affected the result\\\".\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3457}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3480}, {\"ngram\": \"the referee\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3492}, {\"ngram\": \"the hearing\", \"from\": 3503, \"to\": 3514}, {\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The court dismissed the appeal last October and said the tribunal's order was then enforceable.\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The court\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3577}, {\"ngram\": \"the appeal\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3598}, {\"ngram\": \"the tribunal's order\", \"from\": 3621, \"to\": 3641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Judge Allison Sinclair said in her reserved decision that she did not consider the referee's conduct was procedurally unfair in any of the ways alleged.\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3671, \"end\": 3678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Engine_Company\", \"score\": 0.9957318110369984, \"rank\": 0.004148644727333298, \"text\": \"Allison\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Engine_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Allison_Engine_Company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her reserved decision\", \"from\": 3696, \"to\": 3717}, {\"ngram\": \"the referee's conduct\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3765}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Judge Sinclair said it would be contrary to law if parties unhappy with a tribunal decision were \\\"simply able to appeal because they did not like the outcome\\\".\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Judge Sinclair\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3833}, {\"ngram\": \"law\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 3866}, {\"ngram\": \"parties\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3877}, {\"ngram\": \"a tribunal decision\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3910}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 3965, \"to\": 3976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Selles, who was originally from the UK, told NZME she was unfamiliar with the New Zealand court and legal system.\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 4093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4016, \"end\": 4018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999886556577174, \"rank\": 1.1303137006374316e-05, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 4058, \"end\": 4069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.5283038003792035, \"rank\": 0.7669660485154501, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"NZME\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4029}, {\"ngram\": \"legal system\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just the way that the court systems work here, we have no specialisation, we have lay people and we see some of the most ridiculous judgments coming out of the High Court, let alone a district court, or you know, a Disputes Tribunal.\\\"\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4261, \"end\": 4271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_Singapore\", \"score\": 0.9019889946728614, \"rank\": 0.10860013568980624, \"text\": \"High Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_Singapore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/High_Court_of_Singapore\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 4106, \"to\": 4113}, {\"ngram\": \"the court systems\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4136}, {\"ngram\": \"no specialisation\", \"from\": 4156, \"to\": 4173}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4193}, {\"ngram\": \"the most ridiculous judgments\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4242}, {\"ngram\": \"a district court\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cottle said he had all but written off the debt but felt let down by the lack of options for enforcement.\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cottle\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4343}, {\"ngram\": \"the debt\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4384}, {\"ngram\": \"the lack\", \"from\": 4406, \"to\": 4414}, {\"ngram\": \"options\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4425}, {\"ngram\": \"enforcement\", \"from\": 4430, \"to\": 4441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said the Disputes Tribunal was good for many cases but even with a ruling in favour, sometimes a claim might be a lot of wasted time because nothing happened.\", \"from\": 4444, \"to\": 4605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Disputes Tribunal\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4473}, {\"ngram\": \"many cases\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4497}, {\"ngram\": \"a ruling\", \"from\": 4512, \"to\": 4520}, {\"ngram\": \"favour\", \"from\": 4524, \"to\": 4530}, {\"ngram\": \"a claim\", \"from\": 4542, \"to\": 4549}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4564}, {\"ngram\": \"wasted time\", \"from\": 4568, \"to\": 4579}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 4588, \"to\": 4595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She [Selles] owes me 15 grand which is not an insignificant amount, but I have sort of walked away.\", \"from\": 4607, \"to\": 4707, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Selles\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4619}, {\"ngram\": \"15 grand\", \"from\": 4629, \"to\": 4637}, {\"ngram\": \"an insignificant amount\", \"from\": 4651, \"to\": 4674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just angry that she gets away with this and there is no real help out there.\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no real help\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no protection for people like me and everyone else.\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no protection\", \"from\": 4803, \"to\": 4816}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4821, \"to\": 4827}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4840, \"to\": 4848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You walk away from the court and then you are in the jungle.\\\"\", \"from\": 4855, \"to\": 4916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4883}, {\"ngram\": \"the jungle\", \"from\": 4904, \"to\": 4914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ministry of Justice's Tracey Baguley told NZME in an earlier story that the Disputes Tribunaldidn't have the power to enforce costsit awarded to complainants.\", \"from\": 4918, \"to\": 5080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Justice\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4941}, {\"ngram\": \"NZME\", \"from\": 4964, \"to\": 4968}, {\"ngram\": \"an earlier story\", \"from\": 4972, \"to\": 4988}, {\"ngram\": \"the Disputes\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5006}, {\"ngram\": \"Tribunaldidn't\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5021}, {\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 5027, \"to\": 5036}, {\"ngram\": \"costsit\", \"from\": 5048, \"to\": 5055}, {\"ngram\": \"complainants\", \"from\": 5067, \"to\": 5079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is because a moneta